$ govctl adr new Test ADR
Created ADR: gov/adr/ADR-XXXX-test-adr.toml
exit: 0

$ govctl adr add ADR-0001 alternatives Option A
Added 'Option A' to ADR-0001.alternatives
exit: 0

$ govctl adr tick ADR-0001 alternatives --at 0 -s accepted
Marked 'Option A' as accepted
exit: 0

$ govctl adr accept ADR-0001
error[E0303]: ADR alternatives incomplete: at least 2 alternatives required (found 1); at least 1 rejected alternative required. Use --force to bypass for historical backfills. (ADR-0001)
exit: 1
